      "text": "IMPLEMENTATION DETAILS:\n\n• CenterAlignedTopAppBar from Material 3\n• navigationIcon: Row with IconButton (Menu) + Icon (Lock)\n• title: Box with 11dp right offset containing ModelPickerChip\n• actions: Box(42dp) with conditional Config (Tune) + NewChat (MapsUgc) buttons\n• When both Config + NewChat show: Config offsets -40dp left\n• Lock icon changes: 🔒 (blue) when offline, 🔓 (tertiary) when web search enabled\n• Config button only shows when model.configs.isNotEmpty() && downloadSucceeded\n• NewChat button only shows when canShowResetSessionButton && downloadSucceeded\n• All buttons disabled during model initialization or inference in progress\n\nFILE: app/src/main/java/ai/ondevice/app/ui/common/ModelPageAppBar.kt",
